name: FONIKS
description:
The Mythical Creatures series introduce 3 most popular creatures. Here it is the LAST EPISODE.

Episode 3/3: FONIKS (Phoenix)

The phoenix is a long-lived, immortal bird associated with Greek Mythology (with analogs in many cultures) that cyclically regenerates or is otherwise born again. Associated with the sun (gold ring behind it), a phoenix obtains new life by arising from the ashes f its predecessor.
